title: Neff Takes Over Us Open of Surfing 2011
description: Neff Headwear was at the 2011 US Open of Surfing. Neff had signings with Theotis Beasley, Tony Tave, Nick Trapasso. Dion Agius and Evan Geiselmen. They also had a photo session with Yo Gabba Gabba.
